(530, 'MTUwNTg2MTMwMDo3MDE4MDoy', 'Use - Food', 'eaten by Fox squirrel in the traditional story Wissakatchakwa', 'Gatschet 1895', '1895', '', '', 0, 0, 'Gatschet ca. 1895, told by Elizabeth Vallier, Miami speaker, with help of Sarah Wadsworth')
