(943, 'MTUwNTg2MTMwMjo2MjA1Mjoy', 'Use - Food', 'gathered for cooking and eating. \"we gathered the mushrooms for cooking and eating, looked like christmas trees with holes\"', 'Walker 2004', '2004', '', '', 0, 0, 'Interview with Gary Shoemaker, 2004; information gleaned from family, friends and neighbors, not necessarily traditional Miami culture, however believes his grandmother mentioned the timing of morels with the lilac buds')
