(1036, 'MTUwNTg2MTMwMzo5NTM1Njoy', 'Use - Unknown', '\"wikapipikwi, . . . a weed called sheep-sour, leaves like clover, white people make pies of it\"', 'Dunn 1900', '1900', '', '', 0, 0, 'Dunn ca. 1900')
